Thats right, we did trade with Germany, case in point... we need to quit trying to make money off other countries.  Who invented the automobile? America.... so the world uses them now.  If the WORLD didn't need oil, Iraq wouldnt have a pot to piss in, much less be able to finance anything.<br>
<br>
Yes  Russia gave them more arms than the US did, because the Russians dont have as many other comodities to trade with.  Russians dont have vast plains where food grows like Middle America, and Technology. and part for water treatment plants, and cars, no shit they gave them more weapons.  Cause that's all The Russians have to trade the Iraq's for oil that the Russians can afford to trade or the Iraq's even want. I am trying not to use, or cut down at least the use of the words... they, we, so you get a clear picture of whom I am talkign about.  <br>
<br>
One thing we can agree on, there is no reason to goto war. And we can agree that this is how I feel about it.  *<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Only one reason I will goto war.  A direct attack on my family and or people.  Don't say Iraq indirectly attacked us before you finished reading..... keep reading... *<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Iran/Iraq maybe not have been perfect citizens in the World, but they probably wouldnt have thier sights set on us.  And even if they did, it would be with a fucken straw and wad of paper.  <br>
<br>
No, America helps countries with the best intentions, usually, but look whats going on, the knife you hand to someone today can be the knife you get stuck in your back tomorrow.   Stop giving out knives!  Even food, look at Ethiopia, we send them food, war lords steal it use it to feed thier forces.. we send troops to protect the food, Americans die, we make movies about it, and Ethiopians still hate us.  And the rest of the world thinks we are blindly medalling in other peoples affairs. America looks like shit all the way around, even though we just wanted to help. And on top of it it cost us money for the bad world press. Think about it.<br>
<br>
So America Should be like Saddam and kill people because he does?  That is the two wrongs make it right argument.  Saddam isn't killing American's... sure he sends money to terrorists who would, but so did/do we... hell... doesnt Bin Laden have a College education for the US or GB? <br>
<br>
N Korea isn't causeing a problem? Well, neither is Iraq, they are bottled up in 1/3 of thier country with minimal trade going on.  Pick a logic your going to use and stick to it.  America Didn't negociate The n. Korean treaty until 1994 I believe was the year... some 30-40 years after the war in Korea.  Clinton was president when they did the agreement.     <br>
<br>
That's right America does give out money, alot of money, but we can't get a unemployment bill signed before people benifits run out in Jan. of this year.  Egypt and Jordan support terrorism how come we aren't posturing for war with them.  And who will be the next target for us?  We need to take care of our own, and stop worrying about other people.<br>
<br>
I love America, I just don't agree with alot of the shit we do.  America is great, but it can be better.  Who cares if a country is communist, as long as they don't attack us, what does it matter?  Who cares what religion they belive in? Oh you say it matters because they indirectly attack us though providing support for terrorist orginization? Well, so did we, over and over again... heck we have our own terrorists, McVie, Dalhmer, Manson, Jones... we have people burning churchs, moques... wheres the love? we have militia running all over thinking we hafta prepair for some kinda war with someone.<br>
<br>
You after WW2 kuwait was a part of Iraq, and was made a country by the British.  In thier(Iraq's) opinion, they were just reclaiming what was rightfully theirs in the first place.  Albiet Kuwaitt is rich with oil, which is why the British took it and labelled it Kuwaitt, and later the Iraq's for the same.  Same deal with Isreal.  WW2 made it a country... many Jews moved there... people their already are pissed.  Can you blame them? Should they kill each other over it? No way.  Why should the US support one over hte other... both cases are a grey area and we need to stay the flock out of it.<br>
<br>
I will respond to more once I get it... *8P<br>
